United Kingdom.title: Harmonized Index of Consumer Prices: Communications for United Kingdom
United Kingdom.notes:
The Harmonized Index of Consumer Prices category "Communications (08)" is a classification of services.

The category, Communications (07), contains Postal Services (08.1), and Telephone and Telefax Equipment (08.2), and Telephone and Telefax Services (08.3) categories and all subcategories therein.
